<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background-color: #FAFAFA; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
        .wrapper { padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 32px; padding: 56px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #F1F1F1; box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); }
        .brand { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
        .brand-logo { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #000000; color: #FFFFFF !important; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; text-decoration: none; }
        .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #EEF2FF; color: #4F46E5; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        h1 { color: #111111; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1.1; }
        p { color: #444444; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 400; }
        .callout { background: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 20px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .callout p { margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; }
        .btn { display: block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111111 0%, #333333 100%); color: #FFFFFF !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 18px; text-align: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: transform 0.2s ease; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
        .footer { margin-top: 56px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #F3F4F6; padding-top: 40px; }
        .footer-text { font-size: 11px; color: #999999; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .support { font-size: 12px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 500; }
        .support a { color: #111111; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="brand">
                <a href="#" class="brand-logo">PrepUp</a>
            </div>
            <div class="tag">System Integrity Verification</div>
            <h1>Initialize Account: {{otp}}</h1>
            <p>Verification protocol required. Use the unique code below to finalize your scholar profile and unlock the PrepUp curriculum architecture.</p>
            
            <div class="callout">
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #111111; margin: 0;">{{otp}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>This code remains active for 10 minutes. If you did not initiate this request, please disregard this transmission immediately.</p>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-text">PREPUP CBT • ARCHITECTED BY CORECBT</div>
                <div class="support">Connectivity issues? Reach our tactical support at <a href="mailto:mercyjay510@gmail.com">mercyjay510@gmail.com</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
